                                        <h3>How much does a logistics mobile app cost in India in 2026?</h3>
                                        <p>Customer-only tracking app: &#8377;3.5L–&#8377;6L. Customer + driver app: &#8377;8L–&#8377;14L. Full ecosystem (customer + driver + dispatcher + admin): &#8377;15L–&#8377;25L. Enterprise builds with ML routing and SLA monitoring: &#8377;30L+.</p>
                                        <h3>How long does it take to build a logistics app?</h3>
                                        <p>A focused MVP (single platform, basic tracking) launches in 4–6 weeks. A full 3-app ecosystem with admin dashboard takes 10–14 weeks at ITD GrowthLabs using our reusable modules. Enterprise builds with ML routing run 16–22 weeks.</p>
                                        <h3>Should I buy a SaaS courier platform or build custom?</h3>
                                        <p>Pick SaaS (Shipsy, Loginext, our productised CMS) for shipment volumes under 3,000/day or for fast launch. Pick custom once you need unique workflows, 100% source-code ownership, or your shipment volume justifies the build investment.</p>
                                        <h3>Will my driver app work in low-network areas?</h3>
